    <div style="background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 5px;">
        <p>Dear <%= candidateName %>,</p>

        <p>Congratulations! Your acceptance of the employment offer for <strong><%= jobTitle %></strong> at <strong><%= employerName %></strong> has been confirmed.</p>

